Log Files
Phone Kavach(Kishan Suvidha Kendra Pvt.Ltd)Phone Kavach follows a standard procedure of using log files. These files log visitors when they visit
websites. All hosting companies do this and a part of hosting services' analytics. The information collected by log fil
